OL,3,CAlderney patients told to relocate to
OL,4,CGuernsey for dialysis treatment
OL,6,FA man from Alderney says his wife's
OL,7,Flife is being "shortened" because they
OL,8,Fcannot access vital kidney dialysis
OL,9,Ftreatment on the island.
OL,11,FIt comes after Guernsey's Health and
OL,12,FSocial Care Committee (HSC) announced
OL,13,Fthat Alderney dialysis patients must
OL,14,Frelocate to Guernsey for their
OL,15,Ftreatment, a period often lasting up
OL,16,Fto three years.
OL,18,FIt adds that the committee will
OL,19,Fcurrently only cover travel expenses
OL,20,Fand provide accommodation for the
OL,21,Ffirst two months.
