OL,3,CAlderney patients told to relocate to
OL,4,CGuernsey for dialysis treatment
OL,6,FHowever, Alderney States
OL,7,FRepresentative, Alex Snowdon, says
OL,8,Fpatients should not miss out on vital
OL,9,Fcare if they cannot afford to move. He
OL,10,Fsays, "I wouldn't want someone not
OL,11,Fhaving the treatment because it was
OL,12,Ftoo difficult to relocate to Guernsey
OL,13,Ffor that vital lifesaving treatment
OL,14,Fthat that person may need."
