OL,3,CAlderney patients told to relocate to
OL,4,CGuernsey for dialysis treatment
OL,6,FAlderney resident, Jacky Main,
OL,7,Fexplains: "My wife, Julie, has
OL,8,Fsuffered with her kidneys all her
OL,9,Flife, since she was a child, and it's
OL,10,Fgradually getting worse and worse, so
OL,11,Fher kidney function is going down, so
OL,12,Feventually she is going to need
OL,13,Fdialysis.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/13
