OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F387A1761757645
OL,3,CAlderney patients told to relocate to
OL,4,CGuernsey for dialysis treatment
OL,6,F"But now what they are saying is that
OL,7,Fanyone who needs dialysis needs to go
OL,8,Fto Guernsey, which means they need to
OL,9,Frelocate to Guernsey. But there is no
OL,10,Fway my wife and I can afford to
OL,11,Frelocate to Guernsey, and why should
OL,12,Fwe anyway? All my friends and family
OL,13,Fare here."
OL,15,FHe continues: "At the end of the day,
OL,16,FJulie is not going to go to Guernsey,
OL,17,Fand I'm not, so what they are
OL,18,Fvirtually saying is if you need
OL,19,Fdialysis, you either go to Guernsey or
OL,20,Fyou stay here and put up with it and
OL,21,Fshorten your life.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/13
