OL,3,CAlderney patients told to relocate to
OL,4,CGuernsey for dialysis treatment
OL,6,F"Julie is alright at the moment, but
OL,7,Fher kidney function is gradually going
OL,8,Fdown, so there is going to come a time
OL,9,Fwhen she is going to need dialysis."
OL,11,FHe added that Alderney residents
OL,12,Fdeserve equal treatment: "Surely we
OL,13,Fare entitled to equal treatment to
OL,14,FGuernsey people. They can get their
OL,15,Fdialysis and be home in a few hours -
OL,16,Fwe should be treated the same."
