OL,3,CAlderney patients told to relocate to
OL,4,CGuernsey for dialysis treatment
OL,6,FDialysis kidney treatment was last
OL,7,Fprovided in Alderney in 2016, but
OL,8,FGuernsey's Committee for Health and
OL,9,FSocial Care say the decision to end on-
OL,10,Fisland treatment follows challenges
OL,11,Fwith staffing, equipment, the supply
OL,12,Fchain and clinical support, adding
OL,13,Fthere are too many risks.
