OL,3,CAlderney patients told to relocate to
OL,4,CGuernsey for dialysis treatment
OL,6,FStaffing: The Committee say it has
OL,7,Funstable staffing following a matron
OL,8,Fleaving in August 2024, and is without
OL,9,Fa replacement at the same level. There
OL,10,Fhas also been an increased use of
OL,11,Fagency staff due to long-term
OL,12,Fsickness, and major flooring work in
OL,13,Fthe Guernsey renal unit will further
OL,14,Fimpact staffing and patients.
OL,16,FSupply Chain: Issues with procurement
OL,17,Fand supply chain for critical
OL,18,Fconsumables to the Guernsey satellite
OL,19,Funit, and Alderney faces additional
OL,20,Frisks due to exposure to delivery
OL,21,Fdelays from adverse weather.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/13
