OL,3,CAlderney patients told to relocate to
OL,4,CGuernsey for dialysis treatment
OL,6,FEquipment: Guernsey has a technical
OL,7,Fteam and contingencies for equipment
OL,8,Ffailures, which Alderney do not.
OL,10,FClinical Support: Guernsey staff are
OL,11,Fspecifically trained for renal
OL,12,Fpatients and supported by a
OL,13,Fnephrologist.
OL,15,FWhat about the cost?
OL,17,FIn response to a written question by
OL,18,FAlex Snowdon, the Committee for Health
OL,19,Fand Social Care says it will fund the
OL,20,Fpatient's travel to Guernsey and the
OL,21,Faccommodation for the first two months.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/13
