OL,3,CAlderney patients told to relocate to
OL,4,CGuernsey for dialysis treatment
OL,6,FHowever, Alderney patients will then
OL,7,Fneed to find accommodation within
OL,8,FGuernsey's local market, and they are
OL,9,Fadvised to liaise with the Income
OL,10,FSupport team if they need further
OL,11,Fsupport.
OL,13,FWhilst Alex Snowdon says he
OL,14,Funderstands the decision, it is
OL,15,Fsomething he would like to remain
OL,16,Funder review.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G9/13
