OL,3,CAlderney patients told to relocate to
OL,4,CGuernsey for dialysis treatment
OL,6,FHe explains: "I do respect the
OL,7,Finformation that HSC professionals
OL,8,Fhave given about the difficulties of
OL,9,Fproviding dialysis on Alderney. But I
OL,10,Fthink we need to make sure all the
OL,11,Fsupport is in place for anyone going
OL,12,Fthrough a very difficult period in
OL,13,Fsomeone's life, it could be any of us
OL,14,Fif we are quite honest in the future.
OL,16,F"It is a traumatic thing to be taken
OL,17,Faway from the island community when
OL,18,Fyou are born locally and are a local
OL,19,Fperson to the island."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G10/13
