OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F387A1761757645
OL,3,CAlderney patients told to relocate to
OL,4,CGuernsey for dialysis treatment
OL,6,F"Ideally, it would be wonderful (to
OL,7,Fhave dialysis treatment on the
OL,8,Fisland), but the professionals in
OL,9,FGuernsey, whom I greatly respect, say
OL,10,Fthat it can't be provided at the
OL,11,Fmoment, so I think it is really
OL,12,Fimportant that it is kept under review
OL,13,Fin case anything changes in the future
OL,14,Fwhen that service could be provided."
OL,16,FAlex Snowdon stresses the importance
OL,17,Fof support. He says, "We need to make
OL,18,Fsure the support is there and that
OL,19,Fthere is accommodation, that family
OL,20,Fand friends can visit them because it
OL,21,Fis a very isolating thing to be told.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
