OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F387A1761757645
OL,3,CAlderney patients told to relocate to
OL,4,CGuernsey for dialysis treatment
OL,6,F"You have lived all your life to
OL,7,Fsuddenly up sticks and move to
OL,8,FGuernsey for your treatment, and
OL,9,Fbasically say goodbye to Alderney. It
OL,10,Fis a really difficult position to be
OL,11,Fin.
OL,13,F"Guernsey needs to look at the tax
OL,14,Fsituation, no matter what that is, to
OL,15,Fwork out how it can provide services
OL,16,Fto the whole of the Bailiwick.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G12/13
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
