PN,38713
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F387A1761757645
OL,3,CAlderney patients told to relocate to
OL,4,CGuernsey for dialysis treatment
OL,6,F"So I think, whether it's to talk
OL,7,Fabout some kind of taxation or
OL,8,Fbalancing the books for the States of
OL,9,FGuernsey, it's essential so that all
OL,10,Fbailiwick services and infrastructure
OL,11,Fcan be supported moving forward.
OL,13,F"We can't really have services
OL,14,Fdisappearing from Alderney otherwise,
OL,15,Fhow does a community live on a small
OL,16,Fisland? We have an ageing demographic
OL,17,Facross the whole of the Channel
OL,18,FIslands, and it's important that we
OL,19,Fsupport them and that the services are
OL,20,Fthere."
